      "content": "wait i think i'm getting confused. you mentioned \"moving up 3 semitones\" and \"going around the circle\". can you just explain the actual pattern or the way the cycle repeats? like how the sharps and flats change as you move through it? it feels like there's a specific sequence or loop to it.",
